FRUITS VS ZOMBIES

    1. What the game is about? 
The game is about having fruits knocking out zombies who are trying to avoid getting hit. 
    2. Why do you want to build this game?
 I want to build this game because I want to able to step out my comfort zone and creating something entertaining with a bit of challenge
    3. What type of interaction are in the game? You use a mouse and left click to hold aim and release to shoot. 
    4. What is the win and lose condition? 
The win is infinite and it has 21 rounds but in order for you to advance you are going to have too complete each level .The more you play, the more challenging it will be. 


